## Conclusion

These five insights turn the Millennium Guitar from a symbolic instrument into a portable reasoning engine. They are now woven into the Hogge Attractor, Story-Safe Kernel, Arctic Framework, Prime–Zero Field, Quantum Microscope, Dragonfly, Spider, Orpheus Node, and PantheonOS narrative architecture.

**The Millennium Guitar gave us the tuning. Insight-MG gave us the music.**

